@pdeva You are hitting some casing problems. I suspect your queries for totaltime and callcount will not return anything. You can either specify all the dimensions of your data set, or lower case the following on your schema.

```
    {
      "type": "longSum",
      "name": "callCount",
      "fieldName": "callCount"
    },
    {
      "type": "doubleSum",
      "name": "totalTime",
      "fieldName": "totalTime"
    },
```
